### NduthiRide — Map / Geocoding / Routing endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@userToken = <paste_access_token_here>

### ─── Forward geocode (address → coordinates) ───────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/geocode?q=Westlands%20Nairobi
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Reverse geocode (coordinates → address) ───────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/reverse-geocode?lat=-1.2634&lng=36.8030
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Get route between two points ──────────────────────────
### Returns distance (km), duration (mins), and polyline coordinates
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/directions?originLat=-1.2921&originLng=36.8219&destLat=-1.3000&destLng=36.8500
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Get ETA between two points ────────────────────────────
### Falls back to Haversine / 25 km/h estimate if Mapbox is unavailable
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/eta?originLat=-1.2921&originLng=36.8219&destLat=-1.3000&destLng=36.8500
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
